Class DefaultCapabilitiesBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paypal.selion.platform.grid.browsercapabilities.DefaultCapabilitiesBuilder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdditionalSauceCapabilitiesBuilder, UserCapabilitiesBuilder

    public abstract class DefaultCapabilitiesBuilder
extends Object
    This class will create instance of DesiredCapabilities which is pre-filled with all the common properties that are considered de-facto for all browsers.
